  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I have heard whispers here in #m10005000# that you have become a true Arcforger. It stirred my curiosity, and now I wish to see the truth with my own eyes. I see honesty in them… but, can you prove your mastery to me?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Excellent—your spirit remains passionate as ever. Go to the outskirts of #m10005000#, defeat #r#o19#s#k, and craft #b1 #t4020106##k to bring back to me. I shall wait here."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Ah… it seems your mind is not yet prepared."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Now then… let me see. Ho… this #t4020106# is crafted with remarkable precision and beauty. In some ways, it may even surpass my own work. You have earned my admiration—so I must give you a gift worthy of your achievement."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This #t4130001# is a special item. When used in the making of scrolls, it can produce scrolls far more powerful than ordinary ones. But be warned: such power is unstable—while the effects grow stronger, the chance of success falls. A path of risk and reward."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you wish to test the limits of your Arcforging skill, I encourage you to use it. Continue your training with dedication, and your wisdom will deepen."
        }
      },
